{
  "stem": "7069.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I came [INAUDIBLE], it was 13 and under.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We want you to understand that these children will be put into facilities that they will be well taken care of.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For the, for the infants that I see some of you have, there will be nurseries.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For the other kids of, of that age, there will be kindergartens.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then for, for the kids of 13 and a little under, around that, we have school facilities.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But to be sure, before anything happens at all, we want you to understand that they, they will be passed by a, by a, past a medical team.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And whatever they need for medical treatments and, and attention, they will get.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So therefore, we want you to take a few minutes now and explain this to the children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Say goodbye to them, and send them over here to the other side of the ramp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And by the way, don't forget to point out to them that maybe not this weekend, but the next weekend you will be able to visit them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you be sure to explain this to the smaller children particularly, so that they will grasp that, and so on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So take your-- take some time now and do that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, the time was up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And nothing had happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nothing had moved.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The guy goes to his megaphone, well, listen now, we are not hungry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We have our food here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But you guys want to eat, don't you?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So therefore, you better get with it, and so you can get to the camp and get your food, dangling this in front, you know?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he says, I give you another little time, so that you can explain this and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
